title: Nature Made, Vitamin D3 2,000 I.U. Liquid Softgels, 250-Count
body_html:
Nature Made Vitamin D 2000 IU Softgels, 250-count

Maintaining healthy levels of vitamin D in your body has been shown to be an important part of your overall health. Nature Made Vitamin D 2000 IU softgels are made with vitamin D3, the body’s preferred form of vitamin D. Vitamin D supports bone, teeth, muscle and immune health.†
